data.name:
We've had many requests for this....SO HERE IT IS!!!
KENTUCKY BBQ BRUNCH!! Starting this Sunday!

Executive Chef Justin Thrasher has created an amazing 
Down Home Southern-Style Brunch menu that will make your mouth water!!

CHECK IT OUT.......

Southern Eggs Benedict
Two poached eggs set atop a bed of braised collard greens, a fresh buttermilk biscuit lightly grilled and topped with crumbled bacon and a light cheese sauce.

Smoked Brisket Omelet
A fluffy three-egg omelet filled with a mixture of our house smoked brisket, shaved jalapeno, red onion, pepper, cilantro and crumbled provolone cheese.

Watermelon Mint Chicken Salad Platter
Fresh watermelon, cucumber, citrus and mint marinated in a light vinaigrette topped with a heaping scoop of our very own smoked turmeric chicken salad. Served with your choice of dressing on the side.

Home-style Chicken & Waffles
A warm, fresh made Belgian-style waffle batter stacked with three crispy fried chicken wings, bourbon maple syrup, fresh whipped cream and a light praline dusting.

Georgia Peach, Strawberry & Herb Bruschetta
Cinnamon and sugar spiced brioche toast points topped with diced Georgia peach, Florida strawberry, basil, mint, red onion and fresh tomato. Drizzled with a white balsamic reduction.

Citrus & Mango Pulled Pork Parfait
Our very own “9 hour” smoked pulled pork layered with coleslaw, Bobbi Sue BBQ sauce, sliced pickle, jalapeno and a citrus, mango, and moonshine raisin chutney.

Good Ol’ Fashioned Chicken & Biscuits
Battered fried chicken breast served with our hand-stamped buttermilk biscuits, peppered sausage gravy and a side of Red Eye for your drizzlin’ pleasure. 

Deep South Fish & Grits
Hand breaded baby catfish fillets served atop our own cheddar cheese grits with arugula, remoulade sauce, lemon and tabasco honey on the side.

Chef’s Carving Board
In good fashion, we are, after all a Southern BBQ restaurant, therefore, no brunch would be complete without a sampler of our Hickory house smoked goodness… meats that is! Choose between: pulled pork, pork tenderloin, Texas beef brisket, smoked sausage, white or dark chicken, Duroc baby back ribs or our award-winning St. Louis style ribs.

Adults $20.00
Kids $8.00
